Lua canvas
----------

This is a strict implementation of the NCLua 'canvas' module based on DirectFB.
This module is part of the Ginga middleware specification. 

For more information check
http://www.lua.inf.puc-rio.br/~francisco/nclua/referencia/canvas.html

Lua event
---------

This is NOT a strict implementation of the NCLua 'event' module, based on DirectFB.
However, it is based on the interface and implements similar behavior. 

For more information check
http://www.lua.inf.puc-rio.br/~francisco/nclua/referencia/event.html.
